{"tid":682110,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[男人心事]EX搵我打友誼波 好失望...","createTime":"2018-05-28T14:48:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-05T12:19:47.000Z","uid":98507,"like":336,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"fff9d18e3d7453aca21a8c238dddafb9b7144730","tid":682110,"uid":98507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T14:48:35.000Z","msg":"8年前嘅今日 就係我同呢位EX一齊嘅日子<br />\n估唔到8年後嘅今日 佢會搵返我<br />\n寒暄幾句後 佢就暗示我去佢度過夜<br />\n好失望...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想當初我壓抑自己 唔去做一樣大部份男人都會做嘅野<br />\n就係希望佢可以保持呢份純真純潔<br />\n<br />\n分手後 好多人都話佢變得open左<br />\n但我仍然堅信佢嘅內心係唔會變<br />\n可惜呢刻 我終於認清事實<br />\n好失望...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n曾經深愛過嘅女人竟然變成咁<br />\n好失望...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n望住佢 我真係激唔起任何慾望<br />\n聽到佢嘅暗示 我雙眼只有無限嘅唏噓同惋惜<br />\n我可以回答嘅 就只有「夜喇 我送你返去啦」<br />\n<br />\n望住漆黑嘅夜空 我不禁發問一個唔會得到回答嘅問題<br />\n<br />\n點解你會變成咁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25570d44ecc6e72c440999f68faf17a841cee031","tid":682110,"uid":5190,"like":161,"dislike":2,"score":159,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T14:51:11.000Z","msg":"俾佢tg我 幫你勸下佢"},{"pid":"928596322ca9b9a7802feccd5cbd7b6afcd6895b","tid":682110,"uid":59569,"like":144,"dislike":0,"score":144,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T14:53:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">分手後 好多人都話佢變得open左</span><br />\n<br />\n唉"},{"pid":"6b8ee927b0a2e01fad25ba34538e18c01b50f748","tid":682110,"uid":62167,"like":113,"dislike":11,"score":102,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T15:03:43.000Z","msg":"塊閪open左 open埋上下右<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"587f1c5d7d4e856b2b8b17d290d1b405da5b8efe","tid":682110,"uid":98507,"like":4,"dislik